00:00:49.240 --> 00:00:51.510
this and tell you all,

00:00:51.520 --> 00:00:54.070
as I have been trying really hard to

00:00:54.080 --> 00:00:55.990
convey to you what the Spirit of the

00:00:56.000 --> 00:00:58.710
