00:00:59.880 --> 00:01:01.390
Whenever I went through the portal and

00:01:01.400 --> 00:01:03.190
the Lord allowed me to talk to Sister

00:01:03.200 --> 00:01:04.509
Lucy,

00:01:04.519 --> 00:01:08.910
