00:01:14.240 --> 00:01:16.590
And so whenever I was talking

00:01:16.600 --> 00:01:17.830
about travail, I don't want to

00:01:17.840 --> 00:01:19.710
flippantly talk about it

00:01:19.710 --> 00:01:19.720
