00:01:23.240 --> 00:01:26.310
It's only by the Spirit of the Lord that

00:01:26.320 --> 00:01:29.630
you get into the river to that point of

00:01:29.640 --> 00:01:33.070
travail. And that takes a lot of maturity in

00:01:33.080 --> 00:01:34.310
praying.

00:01:34.320 --> 00:01:36.630
It is something that you cultivate

00:01:36.640 --> 00:01:40.070
with the Holy Spirit. And you get

00:01:40.080 --> 00:01:43.750
there by praying His heart.

00:01:43.760 --> 00:01:46.830
If you are praying the

00:01:46.840 --> 00:01:49.670
