00:01:49.680 --> 00:01:51.750
into that travail that I'm talking

00:01:51.760 --> 00:01:55.070
about. But you don't do that in the flesh.

00:01:55.080 --> 00:01:57.590
It is by the Spirit of the Lord.

00:01:57.600 --> 00:01:59.990
You need to know this. I was

00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:03.750
corrected, and

00:02:03.760 --> 00:02:06.510
I don't want to lead people wrong.

00:02:06.520 --> 00:02:08.990
You'll get people who get flaky, thinking

00:02:08.990 --> 00:02:09.000
they

00:02:09.000 --> 00:02:10.590
can get there by

00:02:10.590 --> 00:02:10.600
themselves.

00:02:10.600 --> 00:02:12.550
