00:02:33.160 --> 00:02:35.710
You are only getting there

00:02:35.720 --> 00:02:37.270
through the Holy Spirit, through

00:02:37.280 --> 00:02:38.990
intercession.

00:02:39.000 --> 00:02:40.230
So, you're not going to

00:02:40.230 --> 00:02:40.240
automatically

00:02:40.240 --> 00:02:42.110
sit on your

00:02:42.120 --> 00:02:43.830
