00:03:51.000 --> 00:03:52.510
something where people ask, "Well,

00:03:52.520 --> 00:03:54.670
Brandon, how do I get there?"You get

00:03:54.680 --> 00:03:56.430
there by praying in the Spirit,

00:03:56.440 --> 00:03:58.350
