00:17:44.080 --> 00:17:46.830
Revival never starts in the sanctuary.

00:17:46.840 --> 00:17:49.590
It starts in the secret place. It erupts

00:17:49.600 --> 00:17:52.510
from groaning rooms. It is born on the

00:17:52.520 --> 00:17:55.630
bathroom floor at 3 a.m. It flows

00:17:55.640 --> 00:17:58.710
from the agony of divine burden and the

00:17:58.720 --> 00:18:01.790
joy of answered travail. And the reason

00:18:01.800 --> 00:18:03.950
we've seen so many shallow flames in

00:18:03.960 --> 00:18:06.270
recent years is because the furnace of

00:18:06.280 --> 00:18:08.910
intercession has gone cold. Well, I'm

00:18:08.920 --> 00:18:11.110
here to fan the flame again. In the

00:18:11.120 --> 00:18:12.870
chapters ahead, I will teach you what it

00:18:12.880 --> 00:18:15.470
means to prevail in prayer. Not just to

00:18:15.480 --> 00:18:17.910
pray cute prayers, but to wrestle in the

00:18:17.920 --> 00:18:20.470
spirit until heaven invades earth. I

00:18:20.480 --> 00:18:22.430
will teach you how to pray until demons

00:18:22.440 --> 00:18:24.870
flee cities, until entire regions come

00:18:24.880 --> 00:18:26.830
under conviction, until the very air

00:18:26.840 --> 00:18:29.270
feels charged with glory. You don't need

00:18:29.280 --> 00:18:31.790
a stage to shake nations. You need a

00:18:31.800 --> 00:18:36.230
room, a corner, a mat, a mandate.

00:18:36.240 --> 00:18:37.510
If you're willing to lose your

00:18:37.520 --> 00:18:40.190
