00:19:03.400 --> 00:19:05.710
'I wasn't the preacher, but I carried

00:19:05.720 --> 00:19:06.830
the burden,

00:19:06.840 --> 00:19:09.470
the hidden furnace behind the fire.

00:19:09.480 --> 00:19:11.230
You don't need a pulpit to carry

00:19:11.240 --> 00:19:13.750
revival. You need a burden. And I

00:19:13.760 --> 00:19:15.909
carried one so heavy it bent me to the

00:19:15.919 --> 00:19:18.470
floor more times than I could count.

00:19:18.480 --> 00:19:20.550
While the world was looking for a stage,

00:19:20.560 --> 00:19:23.149
I was looking for a corner to kneel in.

00:19:23.159 --> 00:19:26.030
It was there, on hardwood floors and cold

00:19:26.040 --> 00:19:27.870
upper rooms, that I learned how heaven

00:19:27.880 --> 00:19:30.430
responds to groaning intercession.

00:19:30.440 --> 00:19:33.310
I didn't envy Finney's crowds. I envied

00:19:33.320 --> 00:19:35.710
the presence. And I learned early that

00:19:35.720 --> 00:19:38.030
if the presence didn't come first, the

00:19:38.040 --> 00:19:41.149
people would just walk away unchanged.

00:19:41.159 --> 00:19:43.710
What good is a sermon if it hasn't

00:19:43.720 --> 00:19:46.550
been forged in the furnace of prayer?

00:19:46.560 --> 00:19:48.830
Intercession is not a job. It's a

00:19:48.840 --> 00:19:51.750
calling to bleed in secret so others can

00:19:51.760 --> 00:19:54.590
be healed in public. If Finney was the

00:19:54.600 --> 00:19:58.390
sword, I was the whetstone. And my place

00:19:58.400 --> 00:20:00.590
was not beside him on the platform, but

00:20:00.600 --> 00:20:03.350
before him in the prayer room.

00:20:03.360 --> 00:20:05.710
Groaning in secret, shaking in public.

00:20:05.720 --> 00:20:07.910
I remember once arriving in a city days

00:20:07.920 --> 00:20:10.030
before the revival meetings began.

00:20:10.040 --> 00:20:12.830
I didn't go out to greet the

00:20:12.840 --> 00:20:14.870
leaders. I didn't set up the chairs or

00:20:14.880 --> 00:20:17.550
hand out flyers. I found a small

00:20:17.550 --> 00:20:17.560
inn

00:20:17.560 --> 00:20:19.670
with a secluded room and went

00:20:19.680 --> 00:20:22.630
straight to travail. I groaned until my

00:20:22.640 --> 00:20:25.230
body shook,

00:20:25.240 --> 00:20:27.270
and until the innkeeper knocked,

00:20:27.280 --> 00:20:29.150
concerned someone was dying in that

00:20:29.160 --> 00:20:32.630
room. He wasn't wrong. I was dying.

00:20:32.640 --> 00:20:35.670
Dying to flesh, dying to apathy, dying

00:20:35.680 --> 00:20:38.550
to my will. And in that death, something

00:20:38.560 --> 00:20:41.350
glorious was born. An atmosphere so

00:20:41.360 --> 00:20:43.030
thick with God's presence that

00:20:43.040 --> 00:20:44.750
conviction would later fall without a

00:20:44.760 --> 00:20:47.150
single word preached.

00:20:47.160 --> 00:20:49.110
People say they want revival, but do

00:20:49.120 --> 00:20:51.990
they want this? The unseen weeping, the

00:20:52.000 --> 00:20:54.030
burdened praying, the spiritual

00:20:54.040 --> 00:20:56.150
midwifery that leaves you depleted and

00:20:56.160 --> 00:20:58.630
unnoticed. Revival doesn't come through

00:20:58.640 --> 00:21:01.830
talent. It comes through tears.

00:21:01.840 --> 00:21:04.190
I was never invited to the revival for

00:21:04.200 --> 00:21:06.390
applause. In fact, I rarely stayed for

00:21:06.400 --> 00:21:08.710
the services. I had one assignment:

00:21:08.720 --> 00:21:10.950
birth the move of God and get out of the

00:21:10.960 --> 00:21:13.190
way. And if I could be honest with you,

00:21:13.200 --> 00:21:16.190
beloved, I loved it that way. There is a

00:21:16.200 --> 00:21:18.750
sacred joy in

00:21:18.750 --> 00:21:18.760
anonymity

00:21:18.760 --> 00:21:20.910
when you're walking in divine

00:21:20.920 --> 00:21:23.350
assignment. You don't need to be known

00:21:23.360 --> 00:21:25.430
on earth when you're shaking hell in

00:21:25.440 --> 00:21:27.670
heaven's war room. The demons know your

00:21:27.680 --> 00:21:29.470
name, and that's enough.

00:21:29.480 --> 00:21:31.430
Your greatest effectiveness will never

00:21:31.440 --> 00:21:33.590
be seen by men. It will be known in

00:21:33.600 --> 00:21:36.350
eternity. When you pray, fast, groan,

00:21:36.360 --> 00:21:37.870
and birth breakthroughs behind the

00:21:37.880 --> 00:21:40.350
curtain, heaven moves and the kingdom

00:21:40.360 --> 00:21:42.790
advances. Never trade the glory of

00:21:42.800 --> 00:21:45.070
hidden obedience for the fading applause

00:21:45.080 --> 00:21:48.590
of the

00:21:48.590 --> 00:21:48.600
spotlight.'I'm

00:21:48.600 --> 00:21:51.990
going to keep reading.

00:21:52.000 --> 00:21:53.870
'I didn't start on my knees. I ended up

00:21:53.880 --> 00:21:55.910
