00:21:55.920 --> 00:21:58.270
groans that go beyond words,

00:21:58.280 --> 00:22:01.190
intercessions too deep for articulation,

00:22:01.200 --> 00:22:02.710
and they don't come from standing

00:22:02.720 --> 00:22:04.669
upright in religious formality. They

00:22:04.679 --> 00:22:06.550
come when your spirit collapses under

00:22:06.560 --> 00:22:08.790
the burden of God. And I would lay on

00:22:08.800 --> 00:22:11.390
