00:22:13.400 --> 00:22:15.510
music, no spotlight, just the weight of

00:22:15.520 --> 00:22:17.990
eternity resting on a yielded vessel.

00:22:18.000 --> 00:22:20.550
That posture—flat, silent,

00:22:20.550 --> 00:22:20.560
surrendered—became

00:22:20.560 --> 00:22:22.190
my strategy for heaven's

00:22:22.200 --> 00:22:24.350
