00:22:24.360 --> 00:22:26.030
the room itself begins to groan, you

00:22:26.040 --> 00:22:27.350
haven't yet touched the edge of

00:22:27.360 --> 00:22:29.430
prevailing prayer.'Did you hear that

00:22:29.440 --> 00:22:30.430
part?

00:22:30.440 --> 00:22:32.230
Read that again, lover. 'If you've never

00:22:32.240 --> 00:22:34.150
prayed until the room itself begins to

00:22:34.160 --> 00:22:36.790
groan, you haven't yet touched the edge

00:22:36.800 --> 00:22:38.910
of prevailing

00:22:38.910 --> 00:22:38.920
prayer.'You're

00:22:38.920 --> 00:22:41.630
giving

00:22:41.640 --> 00:22:44.310
yourself over.

00:22:44.320 --> 00:22:47.950
It's that complete surrender.

