than just a dating

00:23:58.440 --> 00:24:00.310
relationship that you may have had with

00:24:00.320 --> 00:24:02.790
your spouse. This is a relationship that

00:24:02.800 --> 00:24:05.030
has been tried by fire. When you say,

00:24:05.040 --> 00:24:07.230
'I've been married for over 20

00:24:07.230 --> 00:24:07.240
years,'then

00:24:07.240 --> 00:24:10.910
you can tell me something

00:24:10.920 --> 00:24:12.710
about your marriage. Usually,

00:24:12.710 --> 00:24:12.720
when

00:24:12.720 --> 00:24:14.790
you get to that

00:24:14.800 --> 00:24:16.390
20-year mark, when you start getting

00:24:16.400 --> 00:24:18.669
past that and you go, 'I have been

00:24:18.679 --> 00:24:20.630
through the fire with this individual,

00:24:20.640 --> 00:24:23.470
and we've made it

00:24:23.470 --> 00:24:23.480
work.'This

00:24:23.480 --> 00:24:25.630
is a cultivation with the Spirit of

00:24:25.640 --> 00:24:27.350
God,

00:24:27.360 --> 00:24:30.190
and it will come over time.

00:24:30.200 --> 00:24:33.790
I don't want to ever cheapen it.

00:24:33.800 --> 00:24:35.550
It's not cheap. It's expensive, and it

00:24:35.550 --> 00:24:35.560
costs

00:24:35.560 --> 00:24:37.590
you something

00:24:37.600 --> 00:24:39.910
to go into those deeper realms.

00:24:39.920 --> 00:24:41.470
Whenever the

00:24:41.480 --> 00:24:44.310
Lord says, 'I have a portal,'this is

00:24:44.320 --> 00:24:48.430
hours of cultivation, acceleration,

00:24:48.440 --> 00:24:51.030
and development. It's not an instantaneous

00:24:51.030 --> 00:24:51.040
upload or download;

00:24:51.040 --> 00:24:53.630
it's a process of development,

00:24:53.630 --> 00:24:53.640
and you need to

00:24:53.640 --> 00:24:56.230
know

00:25:00.710 --> 00:25:00.720
that.

00:25:05.720 --> 00:25:08.990
This book is the heartbeat of

00:25:09.000 --> 00:25:10.590
prayer.

00:25:10.600 --> 00:25:12.430
Praying for the lost, praying for North

00:25:12.440 --> 00:25:14.230
Korea, praying for our president.

00:25:14.240 --> 00:25:16.830
I'm telling you, it isn't just a shallow

00:25:16.840 --> 00:25:19.070
little prayer. I interceded

00:25:19.070 --> 00:25:19.080
and travailed

00:25:19.080 --> 00:25:21.510
for the

00:25:21.520 --> 00:25:24.230
nation of Cuba last night. I'm trying to

00:25:24.240 --> 00:25:27.350
tell you what God is about to do even in

00:25:27.360 --> 00:25:29.070
Cuba.

00:25:29.080 --> 00:25:30.350
He said, 'I'm going to shake the

00:25:30.360 --> 00:25:32.910
nation. I'm going to bring the bride to

00:25:32.920 --> 00:25:36.390
my side, but it will come through great

00:25:36.400 --> 00:25:38.710
pressure.'And

00:25:38.720 --> 00:25:41.390
many will call this Ichabod because

00:25:41.400 --> 00:25:43.830
of what you're

00:25:43.840 --> 00:25:45.550
experiencing. They're going to

00:25:45.550 --> 00:25:45.560
say,

00:25:45.560 --> 00:25:47.270
'What happened? What's going

00:25:47.270 --> 00:25:47.280
on?'Because

00:25:47.280 --> 00:25:49.070
whenever you go through a little

00:25:49.080 --> 00:25:50.590
bit of pressure, you think God

00:25:50.590 --> 00:25:50.600
has

00:25:50.600 --> 00:25:54.070
abandoned you.

00:25:54.080 --> 00:25:56.669
That's a testing of relationship. God

00:25:56.669 --> 00:25:56.679
is

00:25:56.679 --> 00:25:57.910
never going to leave you, and He'll

00:25:57.920 --> 00:26:00.110
never forsake you.

00:26:00.120 --> 00:26:02.190
But when you are in a baby

00:26:02.200 --> 00:26:04.390
stage,

00:26:04.400 --> 00:26:06.790
if you have a little bit of

00:26:06.790 --> 00:26:06.800
a

00:26:06.800 --> 00:26:09.870
trial and

00:26:09.880 --> 00:26:12.110
birthing pains in your relationship, you

00:26:12.120 --> 00:26:14.470
automatically think God's not there. I'm

00:26:14.480 --> 00:26:15.870
going to tell you, when my daughter was

00:26:15.880 --> 00:26:18.470
diagnosed with autism, I thought God had

00:26:18.480 --> 00:26:20.710
abandoned me.

00:26:22.600 --> 00:26:24.669
They told us she'll never walk, she'll

00:26:24.679 --> 00:26:26.750
never talk, she'll never

00:26:26.760 --> 00:26:28.910
be potty trained, and she'll never have a

00:26:28.920 --> 00:26:30.230
normal life. They said, 'You're going to have to

00:26:30.240 --> 00:26:32.470
have special needs care for her and

00:26:32.480 --> 00:26:33.870
hospice in your house

00:26:33.880 --> 00:26:35.590
for the rest

00:26:35.600 --> 00:26:37.230
of your life. You might as well give her

00:26:37.240 --> 00:26:38.710
up for adoption and give her to the

00:26:38.720 --> 00:26:40.990
state because you kids are young enough

00:26:41.000 --> 00:26:44.230
you can start

00:26:44.230 --> 00:26:44.240
over.'When

00:26:44.240 --> 00:26:46.750
I came home and wept before

00:26:46.760 --> 00:26:49.590
the Lord, I said, 'Lord, what do we do

00:26:49.600 --> 00:26:50.950
now?'I

00:26:50.960 --> 00:26:53.510
felt He had abandoned us.

00:26:53.520 --> 00:26:56.470
I felt Ichabod,

00:26:56.480 --> 00:26:58.510
like God had departed. I thought, 'You

00:26:58.520 --> 00:27:00.630
told me I'm a healing evangelist.

00:27:00.640 --> 00:27:02.150
You told me I was going to be in the

00:27:02.160 --> 00:27:03.750
ministry.'And

00:27:03.760 --> 00:27:05.390
when He spoke to me and visited

00:27:05.400 --> 00:27:07.110
me,

00:27:07.120 --> 00:27:09.590
He said, 'Brandon,

00:27:09.600 --> 00:27:13.590
Megan does not validate my word

00:27:13.600 --> 00:27:15.230
for her to be healed.

00:27:15.240 --> 00:27:18.510
My word stands alone.

00:27:18.520 --> 00:27:21.150
It doesn't require her to

00:27:21.160 --> 00:27:23.990
have a complete manifestation

00:27:24.000 --> 00:27:27.030
to validate the word.

00:27:27.040 --> 00:27:29.110
I am a

00:27:29.110 --> 00:27:29.120
healer.'Do

00:27:29.120 --> 00:27:31.590
you understand?

00:27:31.600 --> 00:27:33.270
Regardless of your

00:27:33.280 --> 00:27:35.510
circumstances, regardless of what you're

00:27:35.520 --> 00:27:38.669
going through, God is a healer.

00:27:38.679 --> 00:27:41.070
His word stands alone. It's a

00:27:41.080 --> 00:27:42.590
pillar.

00:27:42.600 --> 00:27:45.310
I realized when He told me, 'I want

00:27:45.320 --> 00:27:47.270
you to go and pray for people, and I want

00:27:47.280 --> 00:27:48.550
you to do this,'I said, 'They're going to

00:27:48.560 --> 00:27:50.430
say I'm a hypocrite.

00:27:50.440 --> 00:27:52.830
What are all

00:27:52.830 --> 00:27:52.840
these?'As

00:27:52.840 --> 00:27:56.150
the Lord has brought us along, we see

00:27:56.160 --> 00:27:58.070
the olive leaf,

00:27:58.080 --> 00:28:00.310
just like it was in Noah's time

00:28:00.310 --> 00:28:00.320
when

00:28:00.320 --> 00:28:01.950
he was looking for the flood to

00:28:01.950 --> 00:28:01.960
recede.

00:28:01.960 --> 00:28:04.470
He first had the promise of the

00:28:04.480 --> 00:28:06.630
olive leaf.

00:28:06.630 --> 00:28:06.640
The

00:28:06.640 --> 00:28:08.270
little bird had it,

00:28:08.280 --> 00:28:10.470
and it was like, 'Hey, everything's going

00:28:10.480 --> 00:28:12.230
to be

00:28:12.230 --> 00:28:12.240
okay.'It's

00:28:12.240 --> 00:28:15.070
the first sign of the breakthrough.

00:28:15.080 --> 00:28:17.830
The waters are receding.

00:28:17.840 --> 00:28:19.950
I've seen it time and time again

00:28:19.960 --> 00:28:21.870
with my little girl. And yet, we're still

00:28:21.880 --> 00:28:25.149
believing for the full manifestation.

00:28:25.159 --> 00:28:28.830
When you go through trials and

00:28:28.840 --> 00:28:31.230
tribulations, when you go through this

00:28:31.240 --> 00:28:33.310
and keep on

00:28:33.310 --> 00:28:33.320
pushing,

00:28:33.320 --> 00:28:35.950
fully persuaded that God has your life,

00:28:37.520 --> 00:28:39.310
that's what I'm talking about. A

00:28:39.320 --> 00:28:40.790
cultivation. It

00:28:40.790 --> 00:28:40.800
buffets

00:28:40.800 --> 00:28:43.030
your

00:28:43.040 --> 00:28:45.390
flesh. It's like sandpaper on you.

00:28:45.400 --> 00:28:47.230
I feel like I'm

00:28:47.240 --> 00:28:48.550
going through the valley of the shadow

00:28:48.560 --> 00:28:50.990
of death, and I am fearing evil around

00:28:51.000 --> 00:28:53.350
me. I know you're here, but I'm going

00:28:53.360 --> 00:28:54.590
through a little bit of something right

00:28:54.600 --> 00:28:56.470
now. Hello.

00:28:56.480 --> 00:28:57.669
That's why I'm trying to tell you what

00:28:57.679 --> 00:29:00.550
I've seen come to these nations.

00:29:01.640 --> 00:29:04.149
The Lord said, 'I will hide the remnant

00:29:04.159 --> 00:29:07.070
in the cleft of the rock,

00:29:07.070 --> 00:29:07.080
Brandon.'But

00:29:07.080 --> 00:29:11.590
there is

00:29:11.590 --> 00:29:11.600
1

00:29:11.600 --> 00:29:14.470
Corinthians 5:5.

00:29:14.480 --> 00:29:17.830
There is a pride that has set in, and

00:29:17.840 --> 00:29:19.750
he said, 'I'm shifting. I'm shaking

00:29:19.760 --> 00:29:22.030
things, but there will be a glorious

00:29:22.040 --> 00:29:23.790
church.'There

00:29:23.800 --> 00:29:25.950
will be what we are all

00:29:25.960 --> 00:29:28.230
expecting,

00:29:28.240 --> 00:29:31.669
but it will come out of an olive press,

00:29:31.679 --> 00:29:33.990
and great oil will flow from this olive

00:29:34.000 --> 00:29:37.149
press.

00:29:37.159 --> 00:29:39.350
I know what the Lord is telling me is

00:29:39.360 --> 00:29:42.149
coming: a shaking to awaken with what he

00:29:42.159 --> 00:29:44.510
said as of today.

00:29:44.520 --> 00:29:47.390
He said, 'Brandon, an acceleration

00:29:47.400 --> 00:29:48.990
as of the first, and it will start to be

00:29:49.000 --> 00:29:51.750
about space.'And the rocket ship

00:29:51.760 --> 00:29:53.270
shot off today, and he said it will be

00:29:53.270 --> 00:29:53.280
a

00:29:53.280 --> 00:29:57.430
new exploration, a real authentic

00:29:57.430 --> 00:29:57.440
one,

00:29:57.440 --> 00:29:58.830
because the last one he said was

00:29:58.840 --> 00:30:02.230
fake. He said a real authentic

00:30:02.240 --> 00:30:05.270
space race is coming.

00:30:05.280 --> 00:30:07.990
Major things are coming, and he

00:30:08.000 --> 00:30:10.750
warned us about it.

00:30:10.760 --> 00:30:14.030
And so I have her reading this

00:30:14.040 --> 00:30:15.670
to you because this is the stuff that

00:30:15.680 --> 00:30:17.350
you have to feed on.

00:30:17.360 --> 00:30:19.390
What you feed on, what you're putting in

00:30:19.400 --> 00:30:22.270
your spirit, will get you ready. You

00:30:22.280 --> 00:30:25.150
can't feed on The View

00:30:25.160 --> 00:30:27.910
or some kind of soap opera to get you

00:30:27.920 --> 00:30:29.870
prepared for where you need to be with

00:30:29.880 --> 00:30:33.190
him. You have to feed your spirit good,

00:30:33.200 --> 00:30:35.230
different stuff. The word of God,

00:30:35.240 --> 00:30:36.990
especially, and then prayer teachings and

00:30:37.000 --> 00:30:38.070
things like that, especially if you're

00:30:38.080 --> 00:30:39.990
called to prayer.

00:30:40.000 --> 00:30:42.070
But as I told her this

00:30:42.080 --> 00:30:45.870
morning, I've had the opportunity

00:30:45.880 --> 00:30:48.790
to go preach all around the world,

00:30:48.800 --> 00:30:50.630
people giving me invitations to go

00:30:50.640 --> 00:30:53.910
preach in Australia, South Korea,

00:30:53.920 --> 00:30:56.110
Brazil,

00:30:56.120 --> 00:30:58.070
