00:30:58.080 --> 00:31:00.510
And every single one of them, the Lord

00:31:00.520 --> 00:31:02.710
has said,

00:31:02.720 --> 00:31:04.590
'No.'As

00:31:04.600 --> 00:31:07.110
I sat there this morning, he said, 'I

00:31:07.120 --> 00:31:09.830
