00:31:09.840 --> 00:31:13.870
I want you to go on live.

00:31:13.880 --> 00:31:16.510
I want you to go on YouTube and I

00:31:16.520 --> 00:31:18.750
want you to pray, and that's your

00:31:18.760 --> 00:31:20.190
platform.'And

00:31:20.200 --> 00:31:22.070
I haven't done anything like

00:31:22.080 --> 00:31:23.790
that because I don't know what I would even

00:31:23.800 --> 00:31:26.030
say when I'm called to pray. I don't

00:31:26.040 --> 00:31:27.470
feel like there's an anointing there for

00:31:27.480 --> 00:31:28.990
me to preach.

00:31:29.000 --> 00:31:30.950
But it's like even

00:31:30.960 --> 00:31:32.550
when I talked to Gina today, she said,

00:31:32.560 --> 00:31:34.630
'Brandon, there's all kinds of preachers,

00:31:34.640 --> 00:31:36.190
but there's not a lot of people that

00:31:36.200 --> 00:31:37.790
