00:31:37.800 --> 00:31:39.550
You must

00:31:39.560 --> 00:31:41.870
keep doing what God has called you to do

00:31:41.880 --> 00:31:44.390
and stay in your lane.'And I agreed

00:31:44.390 --> 00:31:44.400
because

00:31:44.400 --> 00:31:47.190
I've warned her about it.

00:31:47.200 --> 00:31:49.350
You know, Lord, I have all this

00:31:49.360 --> 00:31:51.870
stuff, but it's about bringing it like this

00:31:51.880 --> 00:31:53.630
Charles Finney guy, this guy that did

00:31:53.640 --> 00:31:55.630
this. He said, 'I wasn't the one in the

00:31:55.640 --> 00:31:58.310
spotlights. I was the one that was

00:31:58.320 --> 00:32:01.390
praying on the boards in the room.'It

00:32:01.390 --> 00:32:01.400
was

00:32:01.400 --> 00:32:04.110
Father Nash. Is it Father

00:32:04.120 --> 00:32:06.910
Nash? So keep reading, because it won't

00:32:06.920 --> 00:32:09.190
always be that your name is in the

00:32:09.200 --> 00:32:11.470
lights and you're on the stage preaching

00:32:11.480 --> 00:32:13.270
and doing things. You're the one

00:32:13.280 --> 00:32:15.230
cultivating the Spirit of the Lord for

00:32:15.240 --> 00:32:17.430
the revival that took place. And did you

00:32:17.440 --> 00:32:19.190
