00:32:29.480 --> 00:32:31.550
cultivation of the Spirit and the

00:32:31.560 --> 00:32:33.590
Holy Ghost and fire and prayer

00:32:33.600 --> 00:32:35.190
before his meetings, and the

00:32:35.200 --> 00:32:37.430
traveling prayer minister that went to

00:32:37.440 --> 00:32:39.710
pave the way for him? He quit doing

00:32:39.720 --> 00:32:41.790
ministry and outreaches after this man

00:32:41.800 --> 00:32:43.990
died

00:32:44.000 --> 00:32:47.390
because he realized the importance of

00:32:47.400 --> 00:32:50.710
key intercessory prayer.

00:32:50.720 --> 00:32:51.750
And so that's why I'm trying to tell

00:32:51.760 --> 00:32:55.630
you all. You may feel that

00:32:55.630 --> 00:32:55.640
you're

00:32:55.640 --> 00:32:57.350
insignificant. 'I'm in the back room

00:32:57.360 --> 00:32:59.470
rocking in the rocking chair at my house,

00:32:59.480 --> 00:33:02.150
but I'm interceding for my pastor. I'm

00:33:02.160 --> 00:33:04.470
interceding for the evangelist on Sunday

00:33:04.480 --> 00:33:06.590
that's coming. I'm interceding for the

00:33:06.600 --> 00:33:08.750
schools. I'm interceding for this.'But if

00:33:08.760 --> 00:33:11.150
it wasn't for you, sister or brother or whoever

00:33:11.150 --> 00:33:11.160
is

00:33:11.160 --> 00:33:13.070
out there,

00:33:13.080 --> 00:33:14.430
they wouldn't be as

00:33:14.440 --> 00:33:17.070
