00:33:17.080 --> 00:33:19.550
be, because it takes prayer to cultivate

00:33:19.560 --> 00:33:21.870
it in the spirit realm. Don't ever look

00:33:21.880 --> 00:33:24.750
at yourself as not valuable to the

00:33:24.760 --> 00:33:26.550
kingdom of God. You're more valuable

00:33:26.560 --> 00:33:29.510
than the person with the microphone.

00:33:29.520 --> 00:33:31.669
You are valuable to the kingdom of God,

00:33:31.679 --> 00:33:34.550
and you bring so much to the kingdom

00:33:34.560 --> 00:33:37.750
by just being you and praying for the

00:33:37.760 --> 00:33:40.590
nations. That's why we are all coming

00:33:40.600 --> 00:33:42.750
together, and we're all here right now,

00:33:42.760 --> 00:33:44.510
and we're about to start praying.

00:33:44.520 --> 00:33:46.590
But I wanted to give you something to

00:33:46.600 --> 00:33:49.550
