00:33:51.960 --> 00:33:55.550
of God in this last movement.

00:33:55.560 --> 00:33:59.110
Don't get weary in

00:33:59.110 --> 00:33:59.120
well-doing.

00:33:59.120 --> 00:34:02.030
We must finish strong for what God has

00:34:02.040 --> 00:34:04.070
called us to do in interceding for the

00:34:04.080 --> 00:34:06.550
nations.

00:34:06.550 --> 00:34:06.560
Yes,

00:34:06.560 --> 00:34:08.990
when we get over there, we're

00:34:09.000 --> 00:34:11.710
going to be excited for our rewards. But

00:34:11.720 --> 00:34:13.310
yet, just because we don't have the

00:34:13.320 --> 00:34:15.149
microphone all the time, and we're out

00:34:15.159 --> 00:34:17.270
there proclaiming and doing what we

00:34:17.280 --> 00:34:18.710
think...

00:34:20.080 --> 00:34:22.310
you know, those preachers

00:34:22.310 --> 00:34:22.320
are

00:34:22.320 --> 00:34:26.830
successful because of people like you.

00:34:26.840 --> 00:34:28.909
And for all the people who pray for me,

00:34:28.919 --> 00:34:30.510
thank you,

00:34:30.520 --> 00:34:32.510
because I don't think I'd be able to do

00:34:32.520 --> 00:34:34.750
what I do without you interceding for

00:34:34.760 --> 00:34:38.750
me.

00:34:38.760 --> 00:34:40.869
If I could only, just

