but we're so thankful that God has given

00:35:57.359 --> 00:35:59.950
us the wind in our sails to keep going.

00:35:59.960 --> 00:36:03.030
And so, we will finish strong. Like Lucy

00:36:03.040 --> 00:36:04.230
said,

00:36:04.240 --> 00:36:06.750
'Brandon, you must finish

00:36:06.760 --> 00:36:09.230
strong.'And

00:36:09.240 --> 00:36:11.995
I said, 'I will. I'll do my

00:36:12.005 --> 00:36:13.590
best.'So,

00:36:13.600 --> 00:36:16.030
we're so grateful. It's not a

00:36:16.040 --> 00:36:18.470
'sorry for Brandon and

00:36:18.470 --> 00:36:18.480
Diana.'We're

00:36:18.480 --> 00:36:20.950
so grateful, but I'm going to tell

