I'm trying to

00:36:43.200 --> 00:36:44.710
inspire you.

00:36:44.720 --> 00:36:47.365
This is what I'm talking about.

00:36:47.680 --> 00:36:50.510
Okay, go ahead. 'There is a difference

00:36:50.520 --> 00:36:53.670
between loud prayer and groaning prayer.

00:36:53.680 --> 00:36:56.910
Loud prayer is noise; groaning prayer is

00:36:56.920 --> 00:37:00.150
fire. Travailing isn't about emotion.

00:37:00.160 --> 00:37:01.910
It's about birthing something in the

00:37:01.920 --> 00:37:03.310
spirit realm.

00:37:03.320 --> 00:37:05.430
When revival was about to erupt, I

00:37:05.440 --> 00:37:07.510
didn't shout it down; I groaned it

00:37:07.520 --> 00:37:10.910
through. I wept. I heaved. I cried out.

00:37:10.920 --> 00:37:12.390
The Spirit would come upon me so

00:37:12.400 --> 00:37:15.150
strongly that words would fail, and all

00:37:15.160 --> 00:37:18.230
