00:37:18.240 --> 00:37:20.310
But when I arose, the atmosphere was

00:37:20.320 --> 00:37:22.910
charged with heaven's electricity. You

00:37:22.920 --> 00:37:25.270
want revival? Then pray until heaven

00:37:25.280 --> 00:37:27.430
groans with you.

00:37:27.440 --> 00:37:29.830
