00:37:37.240 --> 00:37:39.910
posture. You lay on that floor. You pour

00:37:39.920 --> 00:37:42.150
out your guts. You wrestle and cry and

00:37:42.160 --> 00:37:44.390
fast and groan until the heavens crack

00:37:44.400 --> 00:37:46.190
and the resistance

00:37:46.190 --> 00:37:46.200
bows.

00:37:46.200 --> 00:37:48.630
The early rain doesn't fall for casual

00:37:48.640 --> 00:37:51.910
askers; it falls for violent birthers.

00:37:51.920 --> 00:37:54.230
You don't stand up until hell backs

00:37:54.240 --> 00:37:56.150
down.'Did

00:37:56.160 --> 00:37:58.110
you get that?

00:37:58.120 --> 00:37:59.550
Read that again, that last little

00:37:59.560 --> 00:38:02.390
paragraph. That's it right there. 'The

00:38:02.400 --> 00:38:04.990
early rain doesn't fall for casual

00:38:05.000 --> 00:38:08.630
askers. It falls for violent birthers.

00:38:08.640 --> 00:38:11.150
You don't stand up until hell backs

00:38:11.150 --> 00:38:11.160
down.'Do

00:38:11.160 --> 00:38:13.950
you get it?

00:38:13.960 --> 00:38:15.710
It's not casual.

00:38:15.720 --> 00:38:18.990
How bad is

00:38:19.000 --> 00:38:21.686
your want to

00:38:21.880 --> 00:38:23.670
keep going? And then there's a prayer

00:38:23.680 --> 00:38:25.950
right here: 'Take me, Holy Spirit, take me

00:38:25.960 --> 00:38:28.910
deeper, past words, past noise, past

