connected to yours that I begin to feel

00:38:36.600 --> 00:38:39.349
your burden. I surrender to your weight.

00:38:39.359 --> 00:38:41.670
I lay down my pride, my hurry, my

00:38:41.680 --> 00:38:44.270
schedule. I choose the floor. I choose

00:38:44.280 --> 00:38:46.390
the ache. I choose the birth pains of

00:38:46.400 --> 00:38:48.550
intercession. Until the heavens groan and

00:38:48.560 --> 00:38:52.470
the earth shakes, use me.

00:38:52.480 --> 00:38:54.590
You want breakthrough? Then prepare to

00:38:54.600 --> 00:38:56.870
break. I broke in prayer before the

00:38:56.880 --> 00:38:59.230
meetings ever began. My heart shattered

00:38:59.240 --> 00:39:01.910
over sin. My

00:39:01.920 --> 00:39:04.390
tears soaked the carpets. My strength

00:39:04.400 --> 00:39:06.750
gave out. I collapsed in the presence.

00:39:06.760 --> 00:39:08.830
That was where the real battle was won.

00:39:08.840 --> 00:39:11.030
The enemy doesn't tremble at polished

00:39:11.040 --> 00:39:13.550
sermons; he trembles at broken

00:39:13.560 --> 00:39:17.150
intercessors.

00:39:17.160 --> 00:39:19.110
I never waited for the warfare to show

00:39:19.120 --> 00:39:20.870
up; I went ahead and engaged it in

00:39:20.880 --> 00:39:23.110
prayer before the battle began. I would

00:39:23.120 --> 00:39:25.030
go into towns days early and begin

00:39:25.040 --> 00:39:26.510
confronting principalities in the

00:39:26.520 --> 00:39:28.390
spirit. The ground would shake in the

00:39:28.400 --> 00:39:30.349
invisible realm long before the tent

00:39:30.359 --> 00:39:32.870
ever filled. That's why revival fell so

00:39:32.880 --> 00:39:36.270
hard. It was pre-broken. The

00:39:36.280 --> 00:39:38.150
enemy had already been defeated in the

00:39:38.160 --> 00:39:40.710
unseen realm. You want revival to hit

00:39:40.720 --> 00:39:42.510
like lightning? Then strike the ground

00:39:42.520 --> 00:39:43.910
with prayer before the crowds ever

00:39:43.920 --> 00:39:45.430
gather.

00:39:45.440 --> 00:39:48.190
Every time I broke in prayer, someone

00:39:48.200 --> 00:39:50.030
else walked in freedom. That's the

00:39:50.040 --> 00:39:52.350
mystery of intercession. Your crushing

00:39:52.360 --> 00:39:54.150
becomes their freedom.

00:39:54.160 --> 00:39:56.150
When you bleed, others are born. When

00:39:56.160 --> 00:39:58.430
you fall, others rise. When you break,

00:39:58.440 --> 00:40:00.870
revival flows. If you're waiting for a

00:40:00.880 --> 00:40:02.990
stage, you're missing it. Find your

00:40:03.000 --> 00:40:05.070
floor. That's where the deliverance

00:40:09.107 --> 00:40:09.117
begins.'And

00:40:10.200 --> 00:40:12.670
then there

00:40:12.670 --> 00:40:12.680
are

00:40:12.680 --> 00:40:14.310
prayers after every chapter. It says,

00:40:14.320 --> 00:40:15.670
'Father, break me before the

00:40:15.680 --> 00:40:17.950
breakthrough. Let me never run from the

00:40:17.960 --> 00:40:20.390
pressure that produces your glory. I

00:40:20.400 --> 00:40:22.030
choose to be crushed under the weight of

00:40:22.040 --> 00:40:23.710
your presence so others can rise in

00:40:23.720 --> 00:40:26.390
victory. Make me a warrior who fights in

00:40:26.400 --> 00:40:28.830
the spirit before the war is

00:40:28.830 --> 00:40:28.840
visible.

00:40:28.840 --> 00:40:31.430
Anoint me with preemptive power. Let my

00:40:31.440 --> 00:40:33.790
life be a seed of deliverance. Teach

00:40:33.800 --> 00:40:35.830
me to break in prayer until the

00:40:35.840 --> 00:40:39.070
heavens open and hell loses its

00:40:39.070 --> 00:40:39.080
grip.'It's

00:40:39.080 --> 00:40:41.790
beautiful.

00:40:41.800 --> 00:40:43.710
I think that's good tonight. Okay, we can read

00:40:43.720 --> 00:40:45.950
more tomorrow. Yeah, there was that one

00:40:45.960 --> 00:40:47.870
thing you wanted me to read.

00:40:47.880 --> 00:40:48.710
Okay, read it.

00:40:48.710 --> 00:40:48.720
It says,

00:40:48.720 --> 00:40:51.030
'Intercession begins when you stop

00:40:51.040 --> 00:40:53.670
praying about people and start weeping

00:40:53.680 --> 00:40:56.830
with the heart of God for

00:40:56.830 --> 00:40:56.840
them.'Read

00:40:56.840 --> 00:40:58.110
it one more time.

00:40:58.120 --> 00:41:00.310
'Intercession begins when you stop

00:41:00.320 --> 00:41:02.950
praying about people and start weeping

00:41:02.960 --> 00:41:05.710
with the heart of God for

00:41:05.720 --> 00:41:07.630
them.'Yep.

00:41:07.640 --> 00:41:09.830
And I want to make this clear. I do not

00:41:09.840 --> 00:41:13.030
believe that God put autism on Megan.

00:41:13.040 --> 00:41:15.150
I do not believe that at all. It was my

00:41:15.160 --> 00:41:17.750
ignorance. When he said to me, 'Don't

00:41:17.760 --> 00:41:20.230
get that flu

00:41:20.230 --> 00:41:20.240
shot,'and

00:41:20.240 --> 00:41:22.310
I did it anyway,

00:41:22.320 --> 00:41:24.630
that's when everything went to crap...

00:41:24.640 --> 00:41:26.710
to hell... whatever you want to say,

00:41:26.720 --> 00:41:28.230
it fell apart.

00:41:28.240 --> 00:41:29.590
I'm going to tell you this: It was my

00:41:29.600 --> 00:41:30.990
ignorance.

00:41:31.000 --> 00:41:33.870
God tried to warn me. I knew the day

00:41:33.880 --> 00:41:37.350
when I walked in there, 'Don't do

00:41:37.350 --> 00:41:37.360
this.'I

00:41:37.360 --> 00:41:39.470
knew it. But I disobeyed because I had

00:41:39.480 --> 00:41:42.110
fear of the flu virus.

00:41:43.240 --> 00:41:45.750
Because we had friends telling us,

00:41:45.760 --> 00:41:47.790
'Your baby could be hospitalized if you

00:41:47.800 --> 00:41:49.790
don't get

00:41:49.790 --> 00:41:49.800
this.'You

00:41:49.800 --> 00:41:52.550
listen to the fear,

00:41:52.560 --> 00:41:53.950
and fear tolerated is faith

00:41:53.960 --> 00:41:56.550
contaminated. It was my fault.

00:41:56.560 --> 00:41:59.230
So, it's not God's fault. But what

00:41:59.240 --> 00:42:01.270
the devil meant for bad, God will turn

00:42:01.280 --> 00:42:03.310
around for the glory, ladies and

00:42:03.320 --> 00:42:06.230
gentlemen, if you just lean into him.

00:42:06.240 --> 00:42:08.150
And yes, this has been refining for

00:42:08.160 --> 00:42:10.310
both of us,

00:42:10.320 --> 00:42:13.070
but it was by our own ignorance that did

00:42:13.080 --> 00:42:15.350
