00:42:21.270 --> 00:42:21.280
autism?'No.

00:42:21.280 --> 00:42:24.830
The devil and God do not work together.

00:42:24.840 --> 00:42:26.630
And you need to know that they're not

00:42:26.640 --> 00:42:28.150
up there buddying up together, saying, 'You

00:42:28.160 --> 00:42:29.350
know what? I'll just allow that to

00:42:29.360 --> 00:42:31.470
