00:42:31.480 --> 00:42:34.710
he specifically said,

00:42:34.720 --> 00:42:36.590
'Do not

00:42:36.600 --> 00:42:38.950
get that.

00:42:38.960 --> 00:42:41.470
Don't put that in

00:42:41.470 --> 00:42:41.480
her.'And

00:42:41.480 --> 00:42:42.910
I said,

00:42:42.920 --> 00:42:45.230
'Diana, I feel a real burden. I feel

00:42:45.240 --> 00:42:47.190
bothered. I'll never forget it.

00:42:47.200 --> 00:42:48.470
It was on the way.'I said, 'I feel real

00:42:48.480 --> 00:42:51.990
bothered by this. I don't know why,

00:42:52.000 --> 00:42:54.790
but I just feel this is a huge mistake,

00:42:54.800 --> 00:42:57.390
but I will do it just in case because of

00:42:57.400 --> 00:43:00.430
what we've been

00:43:00.440 --> 00:43:02.030
told.'Stupid

00:43:02.040 --> 00:43:05.470
on our part for ignoring what the Lord told us.

00:43:05.480 --> 00:43:07.870
You know what? It was a life

00:43:07.880 --> 00:43:10.590
lesson, and we learned it. But I'm going

00:43:10.600 --> 00:43:13.590
to tell you,

00:43:13.600 --> 00:43:16.510
I'll never... I'm so thankful

00:43:16.520 --> 00:43:19.390
for her life. I'm so thankful for what I

00:43:19.400 --> 00:43:22.190
have learned and how it has

00:43:22.200 --> 00:43:25.870
cultivated both of us to become even

00:43:25.880 --> 00:43:27.910
better people. And we look at people with

00:43:27.920 --> 00:43:30.150
special needs with more compassion than

00:43:30.160 --> 00:43:31.950
what we ever could have.

00:43:31.960 --> 00:43:34.470
It cost us something. Oh, it did. And

00:43:34.480 --> 00:43:37.390
when we see children with special needs,

00:43:37.400 --> 00:43:40.590
when we see autistic children, we weep

00:43:40.600 --> 00:43:42.630
with those families. And it is not

00:43:42.630 --> 00:43:42.640
faked.

00:43:42.640 --> 00:43:45.390
It is a travail,

00:43:45.400 --> 00:43:48.310
because I know what it's like to be

00:43:48.320 --> 00:43:51.190
there at that level and see where God

00:43:51.200 --> 00:43:53.670
has brought us. We have seen Megan

00:43:53.680 --> 00:43:55.830
be potty trained, and we're seeing her

00:43:55.840 --> 00:43:58.230
come out of where she has been. The

00:43:58.240 --> 00:44:00.790
doctors are even going, "Wow, she's

00:44:00.800 --> 00:44:03.470
come a long

00:44:03.470 --> 00:44:03.480
way.

00:44:03.480 --> 00:44:05.910
She's eating good. Wow, this is

00:44:05.920 --> 00:44:08.590
amazing to watch her

00:44:08.590 --> 00:44:08.600
progress."You

00:44:08.600 --> 00:44:10.310
know,

00:44:10.320 --> 00:44:12.430
we give all the glory to Jesus. But I

00:44:12.440 --> 00:44:15.470
always want to tell you, it was never God

00:44:15.480 --> 00:44:17.470
that did this.

00:44:17.480 --> 00:44:19.590
Always stay on God's side whenever you

00:44:19.600 --> 00:44:20.910
