00:44:30.960 --> 00:44:31.830
me.

00:44:31.840 --> 00:44:33.390
But I thank you, Lord, that you're going

00:44:33.400 --> 00:44:35.550
to turn this into something.

00:44:35.560 --> 00:44:37.110
And it's going to be a testimony to the

00:44:37.120 --> 00:44:38.430
nations

00:44:38.440 --> 00:44:40.470
about the goodness of God,

00:44:40.480 --> 00:44:42.750
that what the devil meant for bad,

00:44:42.760 --> 00:44:45.030
you're going to turn it around for good.

00:44:45.040 --> 00:44:47.910
And yes, I'm going through this, but

00:44:47.920 --> 00:44:50.750
God, you will get the glory out of this

00:44:50.760 --> 00:44:53.710
when it's all said and

00:44:53.710 --> 00:44:53.720
done."And

00:44:53.720 --> 00:44:56.110
so, regardless

00:44:56.120 --> 00:44:58.349
if you blame yourself for maybe a tragic

00:44:58.359 --> 00:45:01.430
car accident or a very

00:45:01.440 --> 00:45:03.710
serious thing that your child has

00:45:03.710 --> 00:45:03.720
gone

00:45:03.720 --> 00:45:05.950
through, you've got to forgive yourself, for

00:45:05.960 --> 00:45:08.950
one. And it took us a long time

00:45:08.960 --> 00:45:10.790
to forgive. As I was sitting there looking at her

00:45:10.800 --> 00:45:12.270
even tonight,

00:45:12.280 --> 00:45:14.630
I looked at her and I said, "Oh,

00:45:14.630 --> 00:45:14.640
wow,"because

00:45:14.640 --> 00:45:16.510
she had a rough day today.

00:45:16.520 --> 00:45:19.310
And I sat there and I went,

00:45:19.320 --> 00:45:21.030
"Well,

00:45:21.040 --> 00:45:23.349
count it all joy.

00:45:23.359 --> 00:45:26.190
Count it all joy.

00:45:26.200 --> 00:45:28.510
I'm not moved by what I see. I'm not

00:45:28.520 --> 00:45:30.550
moved by what I feel. I'm moved by what

00:45:30.560 --> 00:45:33.349
the word of God says."And he said, "By

00:45:33.359 --> 00:45:36.510
his stripes, we are

00:45:36.510 --> 00:45:36.520
healed."I

00:45:36.520 --> 00:45:39.590
am fully persuaded that what God has

00:45:39.600 --> 00:45:43.470
promised, he's able also to perform it.

00:45:43.480 --> 00:45:45.070
You say, "Well, when is the full

00:45:45.070 --> 00:45:45.080
manifestation?"That's

00:45:45.080 --> 00:45:46.990
not mine. I've

00:45:47.000 --> 00:45:48.990
released that to him.

00:45:49.000 --> 00:45:52.070
I trust confidently in the finished work

00:45:52.080 --> 00:45:54.790
of Jesus Christ, and that guarantees me

00:45:54.800 --> 00:45:56.510
victory.

00:45:56.520 --> 00:45:58.790
We keep going to Billy Burke meetings.

00:45:58.800 --> 00:46:01.030
We go and we get a little

00:46:01.040 --> 00:46:03.670
piece of the pie every single time.

00:46:03.680 --> 00:46:06.390
We go and we get a little bit more,

00:46:06.400 --> 00:46:08.710
a little bit more.

00:46:08.720 --> 00:46:11.110
And it's been gradual, but a miracle is a

00:46:11.120 --> 00:46:13.030
miracle. Even if it's

00:46:13.040 --> 00:46:15.070
gradual,

00:46:15.080 --> 00:46:16.790
