00:46:16.800 --> 00:46:21.070
Never take baby steps for granted.

00:46:21.080 --> 00:46:24.670
Give God glory in every step you take

00:46:24.680 --> 00:46:26.590
because it was his grace that gave you

00:46:26.600 --> 00:46:28.430
the ability to take those

00:46:28.440 --> 00:46:30.910
steps.

00:46:30.920 --> 00:46:32.870
